gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.calculation

Enum ValueRetriever

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ValueRetriever>
      • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.calculation.ValueRetriever
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ValueRetriever>

    public enum ValueRetriever
extends java.lang.Enum<ValueRetriever>

    The set of retrievers that extract a particular variable's value from a Patient object.

    Most of these retrieve a numerical (floating-point) value, but GENDER retrieves discrete String values. TODO: this enumeration should probably be split based on this discrepancy.

        Parameters:

        variableEntry - the VariableEntry object to put the retrieved value into

               java.lang.String key)
